---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Impact & Digital Reach | LaTech Editorial Publishing"
  description="Learn how we advance public education through accessible scholarship, ethical digital reach, and knowledge democratization."
>
  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Impact & Digital Reach</h1>
      <p class="page-subtitle">
        Advancing public education through accessible scholarship
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="page-content">
    <div class="narrow-content">
      <section class="content-section">
        <h2>Knowledge for the Public Good</h2>
        <p>
          We believe that rigorous scholarship should reach beyond academic
          circles to inform public understanding and discourse. Our approach to
          digital reach is guided by ethical principles and a commitment to
          accessibility.
        </p>
        <p>Our strategies include:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Making research accessible beyond academia:</strong> We publish
            work that bridges scholarly rigor and public understanding
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>SEO optimization:</strong> We ensure quality information can be
            found by people searching for answers
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Newsletter distribution:</strong> Direct engagement with readers
            interested in evidence-based content
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Social media presence:</strong> Sharing research and analysis
            to foster broader conversations
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Syndication partnerships:</strong> Future collaborations to extend
            reach (coming soon)
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="content-section">
        <h2>Why Reach Matters</h2>
        <p>
          In an era of misinformation and information silos, making rigorous
          research accessible serves multiple critical purposes:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Democratizing knowledge:</strong> Quality information shouldn't
            be limited to those who can afford subscriptions or have institutional
            access
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Countering misinformation:</strong> Accessible, well-researched
            content provides alternatives to false or misleading information
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Supporting evidence-based discourse:</strong> Public conversations
            benefit when grounded in rigorous research rather than speculation
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Building trust in expertise:</strong> When experts communicate
            clearly and accessibly, they demonstrate the value of rigorous scholarship
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="content-section">
        <h2>How We Measure Impact</h2>
        <p>We track multiple dimensions of impact:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Readership and engagement:</strong> How many people access and
            engage with our content
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Geographic reach:</strong> Where our readers are located, ensuring
            global accessibility
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Citation and reference:</strong> How other publications and researchers
            use our work
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Reader feedback and community growth:</strong> Qualitative indicators
            of impact and value
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="content-section">
        <h2>Our Impact by the Numbers</h2>
        <div class="metrics-grid">
          <div class="metric-box">
            <h3>Articles Published</h3>
            <p class="metric-value">Metrics coming soon</p>
          </div>
          <div class="metric-box">
            <h3>Readers Reached</h3>
            <p class="metric-value">Metrics coming soon</p>
          </div>
          <div class="metric-box">
            <h3>Countries Served</h3>
            <p class="metric-value">Metrics coming soon</p>
          </div>
          <div class="metric-box">
            <h3>Newsletter Subscribers</h3>
            <p class="metric-value">Metrics coming soon</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="metrics-note">
          We're building our analytics infrastructure to provide transparent,
          meaningful metrics on our impact. Check back soon for updated numbers.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="content-section">
        <h2>Partner With Us</h2>
        <p>
          We're interested in partnerships that extend the reach of quality
          scholarship. If you're interested in syndication, content
          partnerships, or other collaborations, we'd love to hear from you.
        </p>
        <p>
          <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-outline">Get in Touch</a>
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, #1e3a8a 100%);
    color: var(--color-white);
    padding: var(--spacing-2xl) 0;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 85%, 0 100%);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .page-header::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(
      circle at top right,
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 0%,
      transparent 60%
    );
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    color: var(--color-white);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
  }

  .page-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .page-content {
    padding: var(--spacing-lg) 0 var(--spacing-2xl);
    animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
  }

  .content-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .content-section h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .content-section ul {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-md);
    padding-left: 0;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .content-section li {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .content-section li::before {
    content: "â†’";
    color: var(--color-accent);
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .metrics-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--spacing-lg);
    margin: var(--spacing-lg) 0;
  }

  .metric-box {
    background-color: var(--color-white);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    text-align: center;
    transition:
      transform var(--transition-base),
      box-shadow var(--transition-base);
  }

  .metric-box:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .metric-box h3 {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .metric-value {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      var(--color-primary) 0%,
      var(--color-accent) 100%
    );
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  .metrics-note {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-style: italic;
    margin-top: var(--spacing-md);
    text-align: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .metrics-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(10px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }
</style>
